{
  "stem": "10181.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Next to the wagon, the-- the-- the-- the cattle wagon where I was were the German guards behind us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had, like, a regular-- regular railroad car where they lived, and they had lots of food, at least lots of bread.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was looking for bread.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Bread was the main thing which interested me by that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when we stopped, we were allowed-- we were allowed to get off the train.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all those years, I never spoke German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't want to.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Even if I understood and I-- I spoke, I didn't want to speak German.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I spoke Dutch.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then I asked one of the German guards what-- what was happening.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he said, well, the engine went away to see-- there apparently is a-- a German-- not a German, an-- an American unit in the area.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they went to see what's happening, you know, and if the engine doesn't come back-- back by nightfall, that means the-- the Americans are coming, and they're going to leave.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then in afternoon, they had some-- they gave us-- those who were close by, they gave us some of the bread they had.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They gave it to us, and they left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then I started to walk to the village, and I knocked on the door.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There-- there was nobody outside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I knocked on the doors and asked for food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I guess I must have looked like a scarecrow, you know, because I was wearing clothes which-- which probably was-- even if I hadn't grown much, it was too small for me and was rotting and full of lice.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And-- and-- and you get these-- you know, these scabs on [INAUDIBLE] over.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
